caller_intent: Agent Jamie from Alliance Insurance is assisting client Mary with updating Jocelyn Harris's email address on her Auto Owners Insurance account after she lost access to her Hotmail account.
resolution_steps: Agent Jamie explains that Jocelyn must log in with her old Hotmail email and password to access the account.
If Jocelyn cannot remember the password, Jamie advises contacting Auto Owners to verify identity and reset the password.
Once logged in, Jocelyn can edit her profile to update the email address to her new Gmail account.
knowledge_required: Auto Owners Insurance online portal navigation
Password recovery procedures for account access
systems_referenced: Auto Owners Insurance online access portal
summary: Agent Jamie guided Mary through resolving Jocelyn Harris's access issue to her insurance account after losing Hotmail access. The solution involved using the old email/password to log in and update the email address. The call concluded with Mary understanding the steps required to complete the update.
